OL,3,CMandatory reporting duty introduced
OL,4,Cfor child sex abuse disclosures
OL,6,FTeachers and healthcare workers in
OL,7,FEngland and Wales will be legally
OL,8,Frequired to report cases of child
OL,9,Fsexual abuse under Government plans.
OL,11,FPeople with childcare responsibilities
OL,12,Fin regulated sectors could be barred
OL,13,Ffrom working with children again if
OL,14,Fthey fail to report a disclosure.
OL,16,FThe new mandatory reporting duty was
OL,17,Fannounced on Wednesday.
