OL,3,CMandatory reporting duty introduced
OL,4,Cfor child sex abuse disclosures
OL,6,FIt also means that anyone who actively
OL,7,Fblocks someone from reporting or
OL,8,Fcovers up a disclosure of child sexual
OL,9,Fabuse could go to prison for seven
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FHome Secretary James Cleverly met
OL,13,FCommander Kevin Southworth, the Public
OL,14,FProtection Lead, and Detective Chief
OL,15,FSuperintendent Angela Craggs, both
OL,16,Ffrom the Met Police, at Hammersmith
OL,17,FPolice Station on Monday to discuss
OL,18,Fthe new policies.
