OL,3,CMandatory reporting duty introduced
OL,4,Cfor child sex abuse disclosures
OL,6,FMr Cleverly said: "Sadly what we have
OL,7,Fseen too many examples of is children
OL,8,Fsuffering from abuse and that abuse
OL,9,Fnot being reported and no child should
OL,10,Fhave to endure that.
OL,12,F"What we're saying now is that if it
OL,13,Fhas been brought to your attention
OL,14,Fthat abuse is happening, there is now
OL,15,Fa duty to report that abuse so that
OL,16,Fthe situations we have seen in the
OL,17,Fpast can never happen again."
