OL,4,Cfor child sex abuse disclosures
OL,6,FMr Cleverly also announced plans to
OL,7,Fgive the police powers to stop
OL,8,Fregistered sex offenders from changing
OL,9,Ftheir name.
OL,11,FAnother new policy will require
OL,12,Fregistered sex offenders to notify the
OL,13,Fauthorities of changes to their
OL,14,Fpersonal circumstances.
OL,16,FThe measures will be introduced as
OL,17,Famendments to the Criminal Justice
OL,18,FBill currently being considered by
OL,19,FParliament.
