OL,6,FMr Cleverly said: "This is in response
OL,7,Fto specific calls for change that
OL,8,Fwe've received from campaigners, from
OL,9,Fvictims, from people that I've met and
OL,10,Fspoken to, and it's an important step
OL,11,Fin the right direction.
OL,13,F"We are making it absolutely clear
OL,14,Fthat you have a moral duty, a
OL,15,Fprofessional duty, but of course now a
OL,16,Flegal duty to report where it's been
OL,17,Fbrought to your attention that abuse
OL,18,Fhas happened."
