OL,6,FWhen asked whether people who work
OL,7,Fwith children should be concerned
OL,8,Fabout ending up on the wrong side of
OL,9,Fthe law, Mr Cleverly responded: "Do
OL,10,Fthe right thing, that's all we're
OL,11,Fsaying. Do the right thing.
OL,13,F"If things are brought to your
OL,14,Fattention, then report them. And we
OL,15,Fwould prefer that reports happen that
OL,16,Fcan be investigated and then
OL,17,Fdiscounted if they are not examples of
OL,18,Fcriminality.
