OL,6,F"But what we've seen, sadly, is far
OL,7,Ftoo many cases where abuse was
OL,8,Fhappening, was known to be happening,
OL,9,Fand action wasn't taken. And that's
OL,10,Fwhat we're seeking to address."
OL,12,FIt comes after the Independent Inquiry
OL,13,Finto Child Sexual Abuse (IICSA)
OL,14,Funcovered wide-ranging failings in how
OL,15,Finstitutions protect children from
OL,16,Fsexual harm and exploitation. The
OL,17,FInquiry was established in 2015 and
OL,18,Fits final report ` with evidence from
OL,19,F7,000 victims ` was published in
OL,20,FOctober 2022.
