OL,3,CMandatory reporting duty introduced
OL,4,Cfor child sex abuse disclosures
OL,6,FIt set out 20 recommendations for the
OL,7,FGovernment. In May 2023, former home
OL,8,Fsecretary Suella Braverman said the
OL,9,FGovernment had accepted the need to
OL,10,Fact on 19 of the recommendations.
OL,12,FThe head of the IICSA, Professor
OL,13,FAlexis Jay, previously criticised the
OL,14,FGovernment's response to the report.
OL,15,FCampaigners have also condemned the
OL,16,Flength of time it has taken the Home
OL,17,FOffice to introduce new measures.
