OL,6,FMs Farris, who acted as counsel to the
OL,7,FIICSA from 2016 to 2017, said: "If
OL,8,Fthere were common threads that linked
OL,9,Fall of the children, now adults, who
OL,10,Fcame forward to give evidence to the
OL,11,Finquiry, it was either that they had
OL,12,Fbeen in a position of such a sort of
OL,13,Fpowerlessness as a child that they
OL,14,Fdidn't feel they could say anything,
OL,15,For that they had said something and
OL,16,Fthey'd been ignored."
