OL,6,F"I think finding that right level took
OL,7,Fsome time and it required a
OL,8,Fconsultation, but we're confident that
OL,9,Fwe've judged it correctly," Ms Farris
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"Overall, if you look at the final
OL,13,Fconclusions of that inquiry, their
OL,14,Fnumber one recommendation was that
OL,15,Fmandatory reporting was rolled out as
OL,16,Fan obligation across the country. And
OL,17,Fso I'm absolutely delighted that we're
OL,18,Fputting that into law today."
